4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive AI Machine Learning Engineer course designed for beginners, with no prior knowledge required. Over 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, and various data analysis tools to create predictive models and engage in supervised and unsupervised learning. The program emphasizes real-world applications and offers personalized guidance from experienced instructors, including PhD holders in AI and Robotics. Classes are conducted in small groups (up to 12 people) and are available in English and Spanish, culminating in a recognized certificate. For more details, please visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop